{"article_id":"xXzb85tRuo714xvc","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The court will determine the constitutionality of DOMA ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"which was signed into law in 1996 .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"|","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"REUTERS","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"DOMA on shaky ground in court","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"The Defense of Marriage Act seemed to be on shaky footing at the Supreme Court Wednesday ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"with a majority of justices expressing doubts about the constitutionality of the 17-year-old law","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"banning same-sex married couples from receiving a wide array of federal benefits .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Justice Anthony Kennedy again looked like he could be the key swing vote on the issue ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"possibly siding with the four liberals on the court","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"who are expected to vote","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"to overturn it .","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"But Kennedy ' s concerns sounded different from the liberals .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Rather than a fairness question for gays , his questions focussed on the traditional right of states","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"to define marriage .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"That difference could result in a decision","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"that wipes DOMA from the books","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"and provides federal benefits to same-sex married couples ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"but stops short of declaring","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that all government distinctions","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"based on sexual orientation","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"be subject to \" heightened scrutiny \" by the courts","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"- a landmark decision","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"gay rights advocates hoped for .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"\" You are at real risk","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"of running in conflict with what has always been thought to be the essence of the state police power ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"which is to regulate marriage , divorce , custody , \"","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Kennedy said .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"He suggested","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"the law was \" not consistent with the historic commitment of marriage and of questions of the rights of children to the state . \"","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"The sole lawyer","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"arguing Wednesday for the constitutionality of the 1996 law , Paul Clement , was retained by Republican leaders in the House","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"after President Barack Obama decided in 2011","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that the Justice Department would no longer defend the statute .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Clement said","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Congress ' s key interest","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"in passing the law","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"was preserving the uniform treatment of couples in various states at a time","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"when there where indications","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that some states might allow same-sex marriages .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Nine now do .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"\" All these federal statutes were passed with the traditional definition of marriage in mind , \"","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Clement said .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"\" What Congress says is ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"' Let ' s take a time out .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"This is a redefinition of an age-old tradition . ' \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Justice Elena Kagan said","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Congress wasn ' t preserving tradition ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"but departing from it","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"when it jumped into the marriage issue .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"\" The only uniformity","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"that the federal government has pursued","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"is that it ' s uniformly recognized the state [ definition ] of marriage , \"","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"that the foray into the issue in 1996 was so unusual","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"that it \" sent up a pretty big red flag . \"","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"A short time later , Kagan read aloud from the House Judiciary Committee report on DOMA","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"which described the statute as a way","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"to resist the immorality of homosexuality .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"\" I ' m going to quote from the House report here....","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"' Congress decided to reflect an honor of collective moral judgment","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and to express moral disapproval of homosexuality , ' \"","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Kagan ' s reading led to gasps from and \" oohs \" from many in the gallery","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"who seemed to think","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"she ' d managed a rare Supreme Court \" gotcha \" moment .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Clement said","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"he was not claiming","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"moral disapproval constituted a sufficient basis for the law .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"\" The House report says those things , \"","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"\" We ' ve never invoked [ them ]","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"in trying to defend the statute . \"","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"It was the second of two days of oral arguments on cases","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"related to same-sex marriage ,","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"following Tuesday ' s hearing on a case","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"that asks the court to overturn California ' s same-sex marriage ban ,","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"known as Prop . 8 .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"Wednesday ' s case was brought by Edith Windsor , a New York woman","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"forced to pay $ 363,000 in federal estate taxes","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"after her same-sex spouse died in 2009 .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"If the couple had been heterosexual ,","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"no tax would have been due ,","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"but under DOMA federal tax law treated the pair as unmarried .","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"CORRECTION :","depth":4},{"id":86,"text":"Corrected by :","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"Nick Gass @ 03/27/2013 08:34 PM","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"CORRECTION :","depth":4},{"id":89,"text":"A previous version of this story misspelled Sri Srinivasan 's name .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":179,"left":163,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":93,"right":162,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":91,"right":92,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":4,"right":161,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":161,"left":117,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":95,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":5,"right":94,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":110,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":101,"right":109,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":98,"right":100,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":8,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":9,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":12,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclea